title: My Free Weather 2.10
description:
MyFreeWeather allows you to view the sky in any city in the world and track local weather. Watch the moving storm & weather patterns via Satellite & Radar. Also, view daily and detailed forecasts, local time and date for any location worldwide, plus alerts to severe weather.

Imagine looking at the current sky in your area, Florida, Hawaii, Paris, Vegas, Bahamas ...etc
Free Full Version
No Spyware
Vista, XP & 98
